afternoon /ˌɑːftəˈnuːn/

(afternoons) 

1. N-VAR The afternoon is the part of each day that begins at lunchtime and ends at about six o'clock. 下午 

例： He's arriving in the afternoon. 他将于下午到达。 

例： He had stayed in his room all afternoon. 他整个下午都呆在他的房间里。

